	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yup, this november, RockNES will celebrate its 20th anniversary. I work on this project since 1998.<br />Well, I invite you to join the celebration with... gifts. The main idea is hiding gifts into the emulator, such as a built-in secret game (if you can provide something written in C for compiling with MinGW), or a single wallpaper, a NES demo... or even a message from #nesdev guys regarding the project.<br /><br />Anything is welcome.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /> What do you think?  <img src="./images/smilies/Mfr_icon_homebrew.png" alt=":beer:" title="Beer" />  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_rolleyes.gif" alt=":roll:" title="Rolling Eyes" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


